import "../styles/views/Faq.css"; const Faq = () => { return (

Frequently Asked Questions

What are Magic Peacocks ?

Magic Peacocks are collection of 5555 unique NFT's created with generative art programming where each peacock has unique traits inside the Solana Blockchain.

Magic peacocks are born from golden eggs with special magical powers in the Virtual reality world.They are all part of VR game with a mission to survive from predators and build their powers by collecting treasures around the world.

What is unique about Magic Peacock project?

Magic peacocks Project is first of its kind to use Solana Blockchain and Virtual Reality gaming.

Bringing together two most innovative technologies like Blockchain and Virtual Reality has enormous potential in NFT space. Magic peacock project want to tap these technologies to add value and build the largest NFT community

How do I actually purchase the Magic Peacock NFT's?

Magic peacock NFT's can be purchased on this website on Launch date-Oct30

What will be the price of 1 Magic Peacock??

Presale price:0.35 sol and Public sale price:0.7 sol

How many can I buy per transaction?

1 NFT per transaction

What Solana wallets can I use?

We recommend Phantom, Sollet and Solflare wallets.

Where I can sell my NFT's?

We are going to list on almost all Solana Marketplaces like Digitaleyes,Solsea,solanart,Grail,Alpha art tc.

Who is behind Magic Peacocks NFT Project?

We are team of artists, software developers(10+ experienced),game-devs and professional Blockchain developers. Our team is our biggest strentgh and We are thrilled about the ongoing development of solana and excited to be part of its journey.

How can I mint?

Please follow the instruction in Tutorial page

Step 1: Setup Solana wallet inside brower Eg:Phantom wallet and Load sufficient balance to wallet from any exchange Eg:Binance

Step 2: Go back to magic peacocks main page and connect your Solana wallet.

Step 3: Press Mint to mint the NFT, which will cost x SOL

Step 4: Wait for the prompt to show and accept. You will wait for 10-20 sec for the NFT to show up in your wallet

); }; export default Faq;
